---
title: Jumbo Scallops on Spinach and Tomato Risotto with Fresh Salad and Lemon-Mustard Vinaigrette
description: Nothing hits the spot like a good risotto. This version features jumbo seared scallops atop a savoury sun-dried tomato pesto and spinach risotto that is sure to make dinner time "me" time.
